  if v = 0 then Measure.dirac μ else volume.withDensity (semicirclePDF μ v)
```

This defines the semicircle distribution. When `v = 0`, it's the Dirac delta at `μ`. When `v ≠ 0`, it's the volume (Lebesgue measure) with the semicircle PDF as the density.

